Introduction

Doha is a South Korean singer-songwriter and leader of the boy group XD (formerly XEED).

Doha participated in the 2016 Mnet reality show BOYS24 where he was the leader of Unit White and later part of their promotional unit, Unit Black. He was eliminated in the final round, thus not being able to make it into the debut lineup.

He went on to make his solo debut on August 16, 2021 with the digital single "Dear. My Side under his full name Park Doha. Later in March of 2022, Doha was introduced as the first member of the group XEED. They debuted on December 1, 2022 with the mini album "Dream Land".
